main event: A report from Project Blue Book documented sightings of a spherical object in the sky.
interesting points: The report consists of 3 photos of a blurry, circular shape in the sky., The object is mostly obscured by distortion or blur., No humans are visible in any of the images., The sightings occurred on October 31, 1966., The report is classified under the Foreign Technology Division, AFSC.
witness description: No witnesses identified in the report.
